Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后唾液酵素便和米混合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米中的淀粉便被糖化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是甜味的米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酿了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经变成糖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&\fs20}{\pos(553,267)}A.oryzae：米曲霉\N学名Aspergillus oryzae
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&\fs20}{\pos(782,267)}A.niger：黑曲霉\N学名Aspergillus niger
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也许不是米是水果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水果的话就没我们的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来建造我们的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&\fs20}{\pos(639,317)}P.chrysogenum\N学名Penicillium chrysogenum\N所谓的青霉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒精出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 有酒精呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 酒精里面我们没法住呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒精出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可谓从神谷时代流传的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本酒的元祖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确来说咀嚼米的是未婚女性的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还动了点手脚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加了点卵鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵鞘？
